title: 2013 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 25)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2013 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

There's a lot of hip-hop/rap included in today's bundle, along with a couple of nice releases by Clint Brown, a rather unique non-instrument project by The Como Mamas, Mandisa's new "Overcomer" single, and the brand new Thousand Foot Krutch remix.  I pray it finds a nice home in your collections, and that you're willingness to share it with others (family, friends, colleagues, etc) is just as motivating for you as your desire to download it from me today.

Our year-to-date total is now up to 656 releases for 2013.

This 25th bundle includes the following 29 titles...

 * A.C.E - 2013 - All Christ Everything
 * B-Doe - 2013 - The Controversial Mixtape
 * Clint Brown - 2013 - Judah Nation
 * Clint Brown - 2013 - Together - The Duets Collection
 * Como Mamas, The - 2013 - Get An Understanding
 * Cookbook - 2013 - Uno-C-u Factory
 * Donny Al - 2013 - How Great Is Your Love - Single
 * Evin Amiri - 2013 - While I'm Waiting
 * GS - 2013 - Win Souls Or Die Tryn - With JoeDoe And Speez
 * Hammock - 2013 - Chasing After Shadows - Living With The Ghosts - Deluxe Edition
 * Hammock - 2013 - From The Dust We Ran To Greet The Dawn - Single
 * Hammock - 2013 - Maybe They Will Sing for Us Tomorrow - Remastered
 * J Murph - 2013 - Soulful Leaks
 * JGivens - 2013 - Hopefully This Will Hold You Over
 * Keisha Cory - 2013 - Light Of The Word - Single
 * Mandisa - 2013 - Overcomer - Single
 * Michelle Williams - 2013 - If We Had Your Eyes - Single
 * Raptureraps - 2013 - Better Days
 * River And Robots - 2013 - River And Robots
 * These Hearts - 2013 - Miserable - Single
 * Thousand Foot Krutch - 2013 - Metamorphosiz The End Remixes, Vol 2
 * Tony Tillman - 2013 - The Tillman EP
 * Various - 2013 - The Messengers, Vol 1
 * Various - 2013 - The Messengers, Vol 2
 * Various - 2013 - The Messengers, Vol 3
 * Various - 2013 - The Messengers, Vol 4
 * Various - 2013 - The Messengers, Vol 5
 * We Came As Romans - 2013 - Fade Away - Single
 * We Came As Romans - 2013 - Understanding What We've Grown To Be - Reissue - Deluxe Edition

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - July 2013
